Guide!

Download and prepare to compile CM7 on a x64 system.
follow this guide: http://wiki.cyanogenmod.com/wiki/Compile_CyanogenMod_for_Shadow
but dont compile!

Once everything is ready. Add the folder /olympus to ~/android/system/device/motorola

And add /vendor direct to the root.

Now type | . build/envsetup.sh

Once is finish type | lunch

Select whatever option is | full_olympus

Once is finished type | make -j2

note: if you run to troubles using -j2 simply replace it with -i

good luck!
